{"tid":499052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肉麻對話流出﹗ 「惡港女」疑終向戇男攤牌「冇對你動過情」","createTime":"2017-12-14T11:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T03:24:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":154,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"197b443130cccad972dacea8ffcf3e68395a36ce","tid":499052,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171214/large/1513247130_e3d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171214%2Flarge%2F1513247130_e3d7.jpg&h=daa62022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171214/large/1513243156_1f4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171214%2Flarge%2F1513243156_1f4e.jpg&h=a4bbaea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無業獨居男疑遇上惡港女，見女方稱無處容身而收留，怎料兩人由相伴聊天煮飯仔演變成虐待收場，男方被沸水淋潑，又遭菜刀刀背及刀柄擊打致門牙脫落、頭頂流血。34歲港女伍寧頤今早獲判傷人及襲擊罪名不成立。有讀者報料，向本報提供懷疑是案中男女的肉麻對話，聽到錄音中女方嗲聲嗲氣謂：「水瓶仔，我好掛住你呀，你快啲返嚟陪我吖﹗」又謂：「你係咪好痛呀？你唔好嬲我啦，你唔好唔啋我啦﹗」<br />\n<br />\n不過其後話鋒一轉，女方語氣突然惡起來：「做咩唔聽電話？我問你做咩唔應我呀？」又謂：「你都戇X架喎我發覺你﹗」最後女方更向男方「表明心跡」：「其實我冇對你動過情。諗返轉頭，極其量都係朋友介乎男朋友之間。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171214/57581306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57581306&d=9bzk9%2FbqrlmVNxuJvCm8qTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b06f98ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57581306&h=230db1ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171214/57581306</a>"},{"pid":"5520dae6b4805b7d338cb272da5caf861ea16649","tid":499052,"uid":108090,"like":121,"dislike":2,"score":119,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"仆街港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"